    org.jmock.integration.junit4.JMock
    For JUnit 4 use JUnitRuleMockery
    org.junit.internal.runners.JUnit4ClassRunner
    Included for backwards compatibility with JUnit 4.4. Will be removed in the next release. Please use BlockJUnit4ClassRunner in place of JUnit4ClassRunner. This may disappear as soon as 1 April 2009

    Included for backwards compatibility with JUnit 4.4. Will be removed in the next release. Please use BlockJUnit4ClassRunner in place of JUnit4ClassRunner.

    Included for backwards compatibility with JUnit 4.4. Will be removed in the next release. Please use BlockJUnit4ClassRunner in place of JUnit4ClassRunner.

    Included for backwards compatibility with JUnit 4.4. Will be removed in the next release. Please use BlockJUnit4ClassRunner in place of JUnit4ClassRunner.

    Included for backwards compatibility with JUnit 4.4. Will be removed in the next release. Please use BlockJUnit4ClassRunner in place of JUnit4ClassRunner.
